Use the standard library
This is how to strange_sort_list of lst:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that left is 0
   Remember that right is diff of lst's length and 1

   Do this lst's length times:
      When left is at most right, then:
         Add result to item left in lst
         Increase left
      But, if not:
         Add result to item right in lst
         Decrease right
      End when
   End do

   The answer is result
